org.apache.drill.exec.physical.rowSet

Class TestRepeatedListAccessors

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest

          • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.rowSet.TestRepeatedListAccessors

  • public class TestRepeatedListAccessors
extends SubOperatorTest
    Test the basics of repeated list support in the schema builder, column writers and column readers. These tests work with a single row set (batch). These tests should pass before moving on to the result set loader tests.

      • testSchema2DMetadata

        public void testSchema2DMetadata()
        Test a 2D array using metadata. The metadata also uses a column per dimension as that provides the easiest mapping to the nested fields. A better design might be a single level (as in repeated fields), but with a single attribute that describes the number of dimensions. The dimensions() method is a compromise.
